INSTALL INTRUCTION

1/ Set the database settings in the file "dbSettings.php" in conf folder
2/ Make sure that you have an HTTP Server installed and launch
3/ Paste the game folder 'MemoryGame' into your web folder (depending on the architecture it may be either /var/www or C:/wamp/wwww)
4/ Create the database dependencies by going to "http://localhost/MemoryGame/utils/installDBTables.php" or by runing manually the script with "php utils/installDBTables.php"
5/ Now go to the game web page "http://localhost/MemoryGame/", you should see a grid with card
6/ You are good to go